Abbreviations
CAPS-CA: Clinician administered PTSD scale for children and adolescents;
CYW: Child and youth welfare; CBT: Cognitive behavioral therapy;
DSM-IV: Diagnostic and statistical manual of mental disorders, 4th edition;
KIDNET: Narrative exposure therapy for children; NET: Narrative exposure
therapy; PDS: Posttraumatic diagnostic scale; PTSD: Posttraumatic stress
disorder; PTSS: Posttraumatic stress symptoms; RCT: Randomized controlled trial;
TF-CBT: Trauma-focused cognitive behavioral therapy; URMs: Unaccompanied
refugee minors.
